      "text": [
        "1213 - وَقَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «إِذَا صَلَّيْتَ مَعَهُمْ غُفِرَ لَكَ بِعَدَدِ مَنْ خَالَفَكَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1213 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"If you pray with them, you will be forgiven to the extent of the number of those who oppose you.\""
        ]
      }
    },
